Increasing the minimum wage should be a top priority and bipartisan. 

@TeamsterSOB has played a key role in pushing Republicans to support increased wages and the PRO Act. 

I hope we can make progress and work across the aisle to improve lives. https://t.co/1ajOXRlmBM

Today I’m announcing my bill to provide $10 per day child care and to raise the wage floor for child care workers to $24 per hour. 

It also ensures parents who choose at-home care or kin-care will be fairly compensated for their labor. 

@nik_popli https://t.co/v4vPRKSMLy
